1
00:00:00,160 --> 00:00:02,120
Run!
- Oh, dear!

2
00:00:02,200 --> 00:00:03,680
Run!
- This way!

3
00:00:03,800 --> 00:00:05,160
Go! Run quickly!
- Where is he?

4
00:00:05,280 --> 00:00:06,720
Let's go!

5
00:00:10,720 --> 00:00:12,040
Uncle, where is Vibhu?

6
00:00:12,120 --> 00:00:13,640
What are you saying?

7
00:00:13,720 --> 00:00:16,120
I brought you to this room
to save you from him!

8
00:00:16,200 --> 00:00:18,160
And you're looking for him!

9
00:00:18,240 --> 00:00:20,840
I'm sorry, uncle. Force of habit.

10
00:00:21,280 --> 00:00:23,880
We left Manmohan behind!

11
00:00:24,560 --> 00:00:26,120
Help! Help me!

12
00:00:32,960 --> 00:00:35,360
Uncle, why did you lock the door?

13
00:00:35,440 --> 00:00:37,200
Please let Manmohan come inside.

14
00:00:37,320 --> 00:00:40,400
I locked the door for a reason.
If Khachedu comes inside

15
00:00:40,560 --> 00:00:45,080
along with Mr Underpants,
he will bite one of us.

16
00:00:45,160 --> 00:00:46,280
Why don't you get it?

17
00:00:46,400 --> 00:00:48,200
Perhaps, this is what God wanted.

18
00:00:48,600 --> 00:00:50,400
Angoori, stay strong.

19
00:00:50,640 --> 00:00:53,080
Open the door, Bhabhi Ji!

20
00:00:53,480 --> 00:00:55,040
No! Go!

21
00:00:56,920 --> 00:00:58,800
Open the door! Let me in!

22
00:00:58,880 --> 00:01:01,200
Go away! Fetch!

23
00:01:07,000 --> 00:01:09,520
Why did you leave me alone outside

24
00:01:09,600 --> 00:01:11,160
and lock yourselves inside the room?

25
00:01:11,240 --> 00:01:12,760
If we hadn't left you outside,

26
00:01:12,840 --> 00:01:15,600
you would've bitten all of us.

27
00:01:16,360 --> 00:01:20,200
Uncle, try to understand
what I'm saying.

28
00:01:20,400 --> 00:01:22,800
Vibhu, you need to understand
what we're trying to say.

29
00:01:22,880 --> 00:01:24,880
We can't come in front of you.

30
00:01:25,000 --> 00:01:26,640
Anu, of all people,
I thought you'd stand by me.

31
00:01:26,720 --> 00:01:29,040
Your divorce is final.

32
00:01:30,400 --> 00:01:33,200
You need to throw this man
out of your life, Bhabhi Ji!

33
00:01:34,960 --> 00:01:36,040
Anu!

34
00:01:37,000 --> 00:01:39,720
Oh, dear!
What if he breaks open the door?

35
00:01:40,640 --> 00:01:42,800
Say positive things!
- Positive things.

36
00:01:42,880 --> 00:01:44,520
Oh, God!

37
00:01:44,600 --> 00:01:47,600
Please open the door!
Do it for my sake!

38
00:01:47,680 --> 00:01:50,320
Anita, he asked you to open
the door for his sake.

39
00:01:51,000 --> 00:01:53,080
I don't believe
in all that, Angoori.

40
00:01:53,280 --> 00:01:57,640
It's a wife's duty to do something
if it is for her husband's sake.

41
00:01:58,680 --> 00:02:01,520
Please! Don't leave me alone.

42
00:02:01,640 --> 00:02:04,360
At least, don't leave me alone
when I'm in this condition.

43
00:02:06,560 --> 00:02:08,480
Why are you so scared of me?

44
00:02:09,720 --> 00:02:11,160
I'm Bharbhuti.

45
00:02:11,360 --> 00:02:13,240
Anu, I'm your husband.

46
00:02:14,280 --> 00:02:15,880
Come on.
- No.

47
00:02:16,000 --> 00:02:18,200
You are neither.

48
00:02:18,280 --> 00:02:20,720
You are 'desi ganna ras' for us.

49
00:02:20,840 --> 00:02:22,400
I think you mean 'dangerous'.

50
00:02:22,720 --> 00:02:23,600
You got it right!

51
00:02:23,680 --> 00:02:25,680
Bhabhi Ji, move aside!

52
00:02:46,320 --> 00:02:48,840
Come on! Untie me.

53
00:02:49,040 --> 00:02:50,280
I am not an animal.

54
00:02:51,240 --> 00:02:53,160
You're not an animal.
You're a werewolf!

55
00:02:53,320 --> 00:02:54,360
Mr Tiwari!

56
00:02:55,000 --> 00:02:56,600
I know he's behaving
like a werewolf.

57
00:02:56,680 --> 00:02:58,880
That doesn't mean you call him one.

58
00:02:59,120 --> 00:03:01,160
Anu!
- What?

59
00:03:02,320 --> 00:03:03,520
Bhabhi Ji!

60
00:03:09,560 --> 00:03:11,600
I didn't say anything
when he bit me.

61
00:03:11,840 --> 00:03:15,560
But he bit my wife, too.
That is wrong, Bhabhi Ji.

62
00:03:16,920 --> 00:03:20,680
Mr Underpants, why don't you get it?

63
00:03:21,040 --> 00:03:22,320
Don't say that word.

64
00:03:22,520 --> 00:03:25,760
Listen, Khachedu.
We won't say 'Bhabhi Ji'.

65
00:03:26,160 --> 00:03:28,280
This is getting out of control.

66
00:03:28,360 --> 00:03:30,760
That is because you keep repeating
the same word.

67
00:03:30,840 --> 00:03:32,320
Which one?
- Bhabhi Ji!

68
00:03:34,000 --> 00:03:36,360
Stop it!

69
00:03:37,480 --> 00:03:40,120
Oh, God!
If you stop saying this word,

70
00:03:40,200 --> 00:03:42,480
I won't bite you.

71
00:03:42,960 --> 00:03:46,800
You don't understand
the trauma I'm going through.

72
00:03:47,000 --> 00:03:48,280
What an irony!

73
00:03:48,480 --> 00:03:50,840
Our day used to start
with this word.

74
00:03:51,360 --> 00:03:53,040
Now, we're not allowed
to say that word.

75
00:03:53,320 --> 00:03:54,440
Oh, God!

76
00:03:54,640 --> 00:03:56,960
Bharbhuti is in a lot of pain.

77
00:03:57,080 --> 00:03:59,920
I think we should untie him.

78
00:04:00,040 --> 00:04:02,440
Look. He's 'bleeding' a lot.

79
00:04:04,400 --> 00:04:08,480
If we let him go,
we'll be the ones left bleeding.

80
00:04:08,600 --> 00:04:11,160
You mean to say 'pleading'.
- You got it right!

81
00:04:11,240 --> 00:04:13,240
You keep your mouth shut!

82
00:04:13,400 --> 00:04:15,280
Let this man rot here!

83
00:04:15,360 --> 00:04:16,560
Mr Tiwari!

84
00:04:17,400 --> 00:04:18,520
Sorry, Bhabhi Ji!

85
00:04:20,400 --> 00:04:22,760
Stop it! I'm fed up!

86
00:04:22,920 --> 00:04:24,400
What is wrong with you, Mr Tiwari?

87
00:04:25,800 --> 00:04:28,440
Anu, untie my hands.

88
00:04:28,720 --> 00:04:31,920
I'm very hungry. I want to eat.

89
00:04:32,160 --> 00:04:34,600
No! Don't untie him!

90
00:04:34,680 --> 00:04:37,120
He is not hungry for food!
He's hungry for a bite!

91
00:04:37,240 --> 00:04:39,800
Don't let this werewolf go,
Bhabhi Ji!

92
00:04:43,040 --> 00:04:45,840
What is wrong with you?
Why do you keep saying it?

93
00:04:45,920 --> 00:04:47,400
What is wrong with you?

94
00:04:47,480 --> 00:04:50,040
You won't understand, silly girl.
Drop it.

95
00:04:50,360 --> 00:04:51,600
You need to drop it.

96
00:04:51,760 --> 00:04:54,800
Bharbhuti, I'll get something
for you to eat.

97
00:04:55,560 --> 00:04:57,640
I knew it. I was sure

98
00:04:57,720 --> 00:05:01,160
that in this cruel world,
you are the only one

99
00:05:01,400 --> 00:05:04,520
who has a kind heart.

100
00:05:04,720 --> 00:05:06,560
You are so sweet!

101
00:05:06,640 --> 00:05:09,680
Bharbhuti, my dad says

102
00:05:09,800 --> 00:05:15,000
God blesses us if we feed dogs.

103
00:05:17,200 --> 00:05:19,280
I will get something for you.

104
00:05:19,920 --> 00:05:22,440
I will help you.

105
00:05:22,600 --> 00:05:23,800
Let's go.

106
00:05:24,760 --> 00:05:26,680
Vibhu, don't worry.

107
00:05:26,840 --> 00:05:30,560
I will find a cure
for your condition.

108
00:05:30,640 --> 00:05:31,960
Mr Tiwari.
- Yes.

109
00:05:32,040 --> 00:05:34,280
Stay with Vibhu and look after him.

110
00:05:35,280 --> 00:05:37,120
I will make a few calls.

111
00:05:37,240 --> 00:05:39,240
You... You take care.

112
00:05:43,600 --> 00:05:44,920
So!

113
00:05:45,800 --> 00:05:47,360
Bhabhuti!

114
00:05:48,240 --> 00:05:51,280
Do you remember

115
00:05:51,360 --> 00:05:52,800
how we used to go
to each other's house

116
00:05:52,880 --> 00:05:54,680
all the time in Modern Colony?

117
00:05:54,920 --> 00:05:57,120
Do you remember
what we used to say?

118
00:05:57,280 --> 00:05:58,760
What did we say?

119
00:05:58,880 --> 00:06:00,160
Try to recall.

120
00:06:01,600 --> 00:06:02,960
Is Bhabhi Ji home?

121
00:06:04,560 --> 00:06:06,920
Go on. Bite me now.

122
00:06:07,120 --> 00:06:08,480
You gave me so much pain.

123
00:06:08,600 --> 00:06:11,480
Now, I'm going to make
things very painful for you.

124
00:06:11,680 --> 00:06:13,880
Bhabhuti, do you remember that song?

125
00:06:13,960 --> 00:06:16,720
The song that we used to sing
and dance to in Modern Colony?

126
00:06:16,800 --> 00:06:18,760
Try to remember that song.

127
00:06:18,880 --> 00:06:20,320
What song?

128
00:06:20,480 --> 00:06:22,840
Try to recall.

129
00:06:24,440 --> 00:06:28,520
"Bhabhi Ji! Bhabhi Ji!
Is Bhabhi Ji home?"

130
00:06:30,960 --> 00:06:34,480
"Bhabhi Ji! Bhabhi Ji!
Is Bhabhi Ji home?"

131
00:06:34,560 --> 00:06:37,880
"Bhabhi Ji! Bhabhi Ji!
Is Bhabhi Ji home?"

132
00:06:37,960 --> 00:06:42,520
"Bhabhi Ji! Bhabhi Ji!"

133
00:06:42,640 --> 00:06:44,160
"Bhabhi Ji!"

134
00:06:47,320 --> 00:06:49,760
"Bhabhi Ji!"

135
00:06:57,440 --> 00:06:58,600
What's wrong?

136
00:06:59,280 --> 00:07:00,880
What are you doing here?

137
00:07:01,080 --> 00:07:02,640
We came here you show you something.

138
00:07:04,440 --> 00:07:06,520
I will give you a slap!

139
00:07:06,800 --> 00:07:10,640
Get your mind out of the gutter!

140
00:07:11,200 --> 00:07:12,960
We came here to show you this.
Look.

141
00:07:17,240 --> 00:07:18,480
What is this?

142
00:07:18,560 --> 00:07:21,600
Can't you see?

143
00:07:21,800 --> 00:07:25,120
Can't you see what this is?

144
00:07:27,000 --> 00:07:29,360
We were... We were...

145
00:07:30,280 --> 00:07:33,080
Vibhuti has turned into a cannibal.

146
00:07:33,760 --> 00:07:35,520
He doesn't see us as humans.

147
00:07:36,000 --> 00:07:38,960
He thinks we're live kebabs.

148
00:07:39,360 --> 00:07:43,480
We're lucky that we're here.

149
00:07:43,840 --> 00:07:48,160
Otherwise, we'd be getting digested
in Vibhuti's stomach right now.

150
00:07:52,400 --> 00:07:55,800
Oh, God! Vibhu has spared no one.

151
00:07:55,960 --> 00:07:58,680
Luckily,
we're still alive, Bhabhi Ji.

152
00:07:58,960 --> 00:08:01,400
We want compensation.

153
00:08:02,320 --> 00:08:03,720
Compensation?

154
00:08:04,120 --> 00:08:05,880
Why should I pay you compensation?

155
00:08:06,640 --> 00:08:09,640
Bhabhuti bit you, not me.

156
00:08:09,800 --> 00:08:11,880
Excuse me, sir.

157
00:08:12,120 --> 00:08:16,760
Your manager attacked us
when we were on duty!

158
00:08:17,240 --> 00:08:22,200
What if Tillu and Malkhan
contract rabies because of that?

159
00:08:22,520 --> 00:08:24,480
They're not even married yet.

160
00:08:27,160 --> 00:08:28,880
We have been attacked.

161
00:08:29,120 --> 00:08:32,440
You have to compensate us,

162
00:08:32,520 --> 00:08:34,280
as our boss.

163
00:08:34,400 --> 00:08:36,040
Yes, you have to pay us.

164
00:08:36,120 --> 00:08:37,640
Hang on a minute.

165
00:08:37,880 --> 00:08:41,120
Where is it written that I have
to pay you a compensation?

166
00:08:41,960 --> 00:08:43,920
The one who bit you will pay you.

167
00:08:44,000 --> 00:08:46,280
The animal who bit us
is your manager!

168
00:08:46,360 --> 00:08:49,440
Malkhan, don't call Vibhu
an animal.

169
00:08:49,760 --> 00:08:51,040
Well...

170
00:08:51,440 --> 00:08:52,600
Sorry, Bhabhi Ji.

171
00:08:57,920 --> 00:09:02,480
Oh, dear! Did you all hear
thunder rumbling?

172
00:09:02,680 --> 00:09:05,520
It is not the thunder.
Bhabhuti is growling.

173
00:09:05,960 --> 00:09:09,240
Don't say that word.
Don't say Bhabhi Ji.

174
00:09:10,400 --> 00:09:13,840
We will never say that word.

175
00:09:14,000 --> 00:09:17,120
We will get ourselves treated.

176
00:09:17,200 --> 00:09:18,960
I gave you Rs 10, didn't I?

177
00:09:19,880 --> 00:09:21,360
Use it to get treated.

178
00:09:21,480 --> 00:09:23,360
Excuse me, sir.

179
00:09:23,440 --> 00:09:27,480
Roll up the ten rupee note

180
00:09:28,840 --> 00:09:31,160
and put it in your back pocket.

181
00:09:32,000 --> 00:09:33,240
Bhabhi Ji is right here.

182
00:09:33,320 --> 00:09:36,520
Sir, we were attacked.

183
00:09:36,680 --> 00:09:40,600
We want compensation or else,
we'll quit.

184
00:09:40,680 --> 00:09:41,840
He's right.

185
00:09:42,440 --> 00:09:43,960
No, wait. Boys.

186
00:09:45,080 --> 00:09:48,960
Mr Tiwari. Vibhu's condition
is quite serious.

187
00:09:50,000 --> 00:09:52,360
If they quit their jobs,

188
00:09:52,640 --> 00:09:55,680
you'll have to do
the work of five people.

189
00:09:56,840 --> 00:09:58,800
Hang on a minute.

190
00:09:59,680 --> 00:10:01,520
I will pay the compensation.

191
00:10:01,720 --> 00:10:05,960
What proof do you have
that Bhabhuti bit you?

192
00:10:06,360 --> 00:10:07,760
What kind of a question is that?

193
00:10:07,840 --> 00:10:10,200
Do you expect us to gather evidence
when we're being bitten?

194
00:10:10,320 --> 00:10:11,880
Do you mean

195
00:10:11,960 --> 00:10:14,720
we should have asked him to wait
when he was about to bite us?

196
00:10:14,920 --> 00:10:18,200
Did you expect us to click a selfie
with him as he was biting us?

197
00:10:18,360 --> 00:10:19,760
Is that what you want?

198
00:10:22,800 --> 00:10:26,240
I need proof that Bhabhuti bit you.

199
00:10:26,520 --> 00:10:28,760
If you got bitten by a stray dog,

200
00:10:29,040 --> 00:10:30,320
and claim that Bhabhuti bit you,

201
00:10:30,400 --> 00:10:33,360
does that make me
liable to pay you?

202
00:10:33,440 --> 00:10:34,680
You have bitten me so many times.

203
00:10:34,800 --> 00:10:36,560
Hey! What did you say?

204
00:10:36,640 --> 00:10:38,160
What do we need to do?

205
00:10:38,240 --> 00:10:39,640
Tell us what we have to do.

206
00:10:39,800 --> 00:10:42,680
You have to gather evidence

207
00:10:42,760 --> 00:10:47,720
to prove that Bhabhuti was the one
who attacked all three of you.

208
00:10:48,000 --> 00:10:50,280
I will pay the compensation
immediately.

209
00:10:50,400 --> 00:10:52,240
We will bring you proof.

210
00:10:52,720 --> 00:10:54,680
Let's look for evidence.

211
00:10:55,480 --> 00:10:58,520
We can check the CCTV footage.

212
00:11:06,440 --> 00:11:09,200
Tika.
- Yes.

213
00:11:09,360 --> 00:11:12,560
You may be thick-skulled, but
your pea-sized brain still works.

214
00:11:12,880 --> 00:11:17,320
I got a dog bite
instead of a love bite.

215
00:11:18,080 --> 00:11:20,840
Mr Tiwari will have
to compensate for it.

216
00:11:21,000 --> 00:11:24,320
You did the right thing
by untying Vibhuti.

217
00:11:24,600 --> 00:11:29,000
Mr Tiwari will have
to believe us now.

218
00:11:29,160 --> 00:11:30,920
He has to pay the compensation.

219
00:11:31,080 --> 00:11:33,040
Be ready to be bitten.

220
00:11:33,240 --> 00:11:34,520
You're right.

221
00:11:40,320 --> 00:11:43,200
Come on, Mr Tiwari.
What took you so long?

222
00:11:43,880 --> 00:11:45,160
Take a look!

223
00:11:47,280 --> 00:11:49,400
'Meet the TV that has it all!'

224
00:11:49,480 --> 00:11:52,240
'VZY TV! TV time is back!'

225
00:11:56,520 --> 00:12:01,320
Bhabhi Ji you praise VZY TV a lot.

226
00:12:01,840 --> 00:12:04,400
Every other smart TV works
the same way.

227
00:12:04,520 --> 00:12:06,040
What's different about it?

228
00:12:06,120 --> 00:12:08,720
VZY TV has so many smart features!

229
00:12:08,880 --> 00:12:11,280
If I ask you to bring about
that many changes in you,

230
00:12:11,360 --> 00:12:14,640
it will take you ages to do that.

231
00:12:14,760 --> 00:12:16,240
Really?
- Yes.

232
00:12:16,600 --> 00:12:18,200
What are those features?

233
00:12:18,320 --> 00:12:21,520
With VZY TV you get
one year entertainment subscription.

234
00:12:21,720 --> 00:12:23,320
It's worth Rs 10,000.

235
00:12:23,400 --> 00:12:26,200
More than 22 OTT apps
are included in it.

236
00:12:26,320 --> 00:12:28,520
And it also includes
more than 390 TV channels!

237
00:12:28,600 --> 00:12:32,840
Really? Does that mean we don't
have to pay extra for subscription?

238
00:12:32,920 --> 00:12:34,120
Not at all!

239
00:12:34,200 --> 00:12:39,000
Wow, that's a magical thing!

240
00:12:39,120 --> 00:12:41,840
Look at its bezel-less
and monolith design.

241
00:12:41,920 --> 00:12:44,960
You can hardly see the border
of the television.

242
00:12:45,040 --> 00:12:48,080
It makes the screen appear bigger
and gives it a modern look.

243
00:12:48,480 --> 00:12:50,680
VZY TV is a class apart.

244
00:12:51,160 --> 00:12:53,560
Moreover, it even has karaoke.

245
00:12:55,080 --> 00:12:57,440
Wow, that's great!

246
00:12:58,160 --> 00:13:02,280
I'll put on karaoke and
serenade you with lovely songs.

247
00:13:02,800 --> 00:13:04,240
You can serenade me later.

248
00:13:04,360 --> 00:13:06,760
Think of a way
to boost our business.

249
00:13:06,880 --> 00:13:08,880
Our business will grow
by leaps and bounds,

250
00:13:08,960 --> 00:13:12,960
because VZY TV won't let our guests
leave the resort even for a second.

251
00:13:13,080 --> 00:13:16,400
But for that we need guests.
When will we have guests?

252
00:13:16,520 --> 00:13:18,200
They will come for sure.

253
00:13:18,280 --> 00:13:21,240
As soon as we put up VZY TV,
they'll start coming in hordes.

254
00:13:26,720 --> 00:13:28,720
Oh, dear! That's Manmohan screaming!

255
00:13:29,560 --> 00:13:31,160
Why did he scream?

256
00:13:41,880 --> 00:13:43,680
Bharbhuti, what happened?

257
00:13:43,960 --> 00:13:46,040
Why are you crying?
- Bha...

258
00:13:47,840 --> 00:13:49,560
Do you have coal?

259
00:13:49,840 --> 00:13:51,520
Yes, I do. Why do you ask?

260
00:13:51,720 --> 00:13:54,360
Bhabhi Ji, burn a coal
and give it to me. I'll swallow it.

261
00:13:54,520 --> 00:13:57,400
No, I don't have it.
I've run out of coal.

262
00:13:57,480 --> 00:14:00,040
Do you have kerosene?
- Yes, I do.

263
00:14:00,200 --> 00:14:02,560
Please give me some.

264
00:14:02,680 --> 00:14:05,120
Why? - I'll put it in my mouth
and set fire to it!

265
00:14:05,320 --> 00:14:07,280
No!
I've run out of kerosene, as well.

266
00:14:07,600 --> 00:14:11,040
When will my pain end?

267
00:14:11,400 --> 00:14:13,280
Bharbhuti, how did you get released?

268
00:14:13,760 --> 00:14:14,880
Who untied you?

269
00:14:15,120 --> 00:14:17,480
I just heard Manmohan scream.
How come?

270
00:14:18,080 --> 00:14:21,320
Actually, I bit his buttock again.

271
00:14:22,040 --> 00:14:23,800
Oh, dear!

272
00:14:24,640 --> 00:14:26,280
Why did you bite him?

273
00:14:26,480 --> 00:14:30,080
Because Manmohan was saying
that word again and again.

274
00:14:30,320 --> 00:14:32,520
The word that triggers me

275
00:14:32,600 --> 00:14:35,320
into biting everyone.

276
00:14:35,640 --> 00:14:38,760
Bharbhuti, I can understand
your pain.

277
00:14:39,080 --> 00:14:40,520
What should we do
about your condition?

278
00:14:40,680 --> 00:14:43,400
Bha... No. I won't say it.

279
00:14:43,520 --> 00:14:46,800
I bit Mr Tiwari so many times

280
00:14:46,920 --> 00:14:49,440
on his buttocks

281
00:14:49,600 --> 00:14:51,760
that it looks like a couch
shredded by a dog!

282
00:14:52,880 --> 00:14:57,560
I didn't even spare my own uncle.
I bit him, too!

283
00:14:58,480 --> 00:15:02,400
And I bit you, too!

284
00:15:05,640 --> 00:15:08,080
It's okay, Bharbhuti.

285
00:15:09,480 --> 00:15:12,360
What can we do?
I can understand your situation.

286
00:15:12,560 --> 00:15:15,040
You have no idea
what I'm going through.

287
00:15:15,480 --> 00:15:19,480
I can't say the very word
that was my life's purpose.

288
00:15:20,040 --> 00:15:22,560
I have wreaked havoc
by biting everyone.

289
00:15:23,240 --> 00:15:27,000
I am not a cannibal, Bha...
I'm not a cannibal.

290
00:15:27,320 --> 00:15:30,360
I am not doing this on purpose.

291
00:15:30,480 --> 00:15:33,080
It happens involuntarily.

292
00:15:33,960 --> 00:15:36,560
You know that I would
never hurt anyone.

293
00:15:36,760 --> 00:15:39,520
I'm someone who spreads love.
I'm a lover.

294
00:15:39,640 --> 00:15:41,080
Please love me.

295
00:15:41,160 --> 00:15:42,640
What did you say?

296
00:15:42,920 --> 00:15:45,760
Please help me. Help me out.

297
00:15:46,240 --> 00:15:50,120
Bharbhuti, will you do as I say?

298
00:15:50,320 --> 00:15:52,560
I always do, Bha...

299
00:15:52,800 --> 00:15:54,680
I'll do as you say.

300
00:15:54,840 --> 00:15:57,400
Alright. I'll be right back.

301
00:15:59,640 --> 00:16:01,880
I think she has gone
to get something to eat.

302
00:16:02,200 --> 00:16:06,360
Bharbhuti,
I have 'chased' this for you.

303
00:16:09,040 --> 00:16:12,720
Did you chase a dog in the park
and snatch it from him?

304
00:16:12,800 --> 00:16:15,320
No, I bought it!

305
00:16:16,000 --> 00:16:18,800
You want to say 'purchase'.
- You got it right!

306
00:16:19,600 --> 00:16:23,760
If you put this muzzle on
your mouth, you won't bite anyone.

307
00:16:23,880 --> 00:16:27,640
Even if you hear that word,
you won't be able to bite anyone.

308
00:16:31,640 --> 00:16:33,000
Who knew it would come to this!

309
00:16:34,360 --> 00:16:35,600
How do I look?

310
00:16:37,800 --> 00:16:40,120
You don't look good,
but you should wear it.

311
00:16:40,320 --> 00:16:42,000
You really need it.

312
00:16:43,120 --> 00:16:46,280
Where did Vibhu go?
We had tied him up.

313
00:16:46,800 --> 00:16:49,560
How did he slip away?
Where will I find him?

314
00:16:52,120 --> 00:16:54,680
It's courtesy of those boys,
Bhabhi Ji.

315
00:16:54,920 --> 00:16:56,600
They untied Bhabhuti.

316
00:17:02,400 --> 00:17:04,360
Bhabhi...

317
00:17:04,960 --> 00:17:08,920
Bhabhi Ji, your dear husband
has given me a lot of pain.

318
00:17:09,280 --> 00:17:14,720
The moment he gets a chance,
he bites my behind.

319
00:17:15,120 --> 00:17:16,880
Did he bite you again?

320
00:17:17,400 --> 00:17:20,720
He bit me not just once,
but thrice.

321
00:17:20,800 --> 00:17:23,480
Oh, God! Mr Tiwari, are you okay?

322
00:17:24,280 --> 00:17:25,440
Are you really asking me that?

323
00:17:25,760 --> 00:17:30,520
I can't tolerate this pain.
I'm bruised all over.

324
00:17:31,600 --> 00:17:33,640
I feel as if I might die.

325
00:17:34,600 --> 00:17:36,200
Why are you saying this?

326
00:17:36,400 --> 00:17:39,040
Vibhu's bites won't give you rabies.

327
00:17:39,120 --> 00:17:41,640
Forget about rabies. Right now,

328
00:17:42,160 --> 00:17:45,320
I can't bear the pain, Bhabhi...

329
00:17:45,640 --> 00:17:49,520
What a predicament!
I can't say the word

330
00:17:49,960 --> 00:17:53,320
that brings solace to my heart.

331
00:17:54,280 --> 00:17:56,600
Mr Tiwari, you're mumbling
even when you're in pain.

332
00:17:56,920 --> 00:17:57,760
Say it aloud.

333
00:17:57,840 --> 00:17:59,480
I can't bear this pain!

334
00:17:59,560 --> 00:18:01,120
I'm scared I might die!

335
00:18:01,200 --> 00:18:03,720
Mr Tiwari, don't say that.

336
00:18:04,320 --> 00:18:07,120
Can I help you get relief
from this pain?

337
00:18:08,080 --> 00:18:10,920
Now, you've come to the point.
- I'm sorry?

338
00:18:11,280 --> 00:18:13,400
What's the point, Bhabhi Ji?

339
00:18:14,400 --> 00:18:16,400
I don't think you can do it.

340
00:18:16,800 --> 00:18:18,800
I'm missing my mom.

341
00:18:19,160 --> 00:18:21,160
Every time I was in pain,

342
00:18:21,240 --> 00:18:25,360
my mom would put my head
in her lap and caress it.

343
00:18:25,440 --> 00:18:29,160
She would sing to me.
And my pain would go in an instant!

344
00:18:30,480 --> 00:18:31,960
Mr Tiwari, I have an idea.

345
00:18:32,160 --> 00:18:33,840
Why don't you call your mom?

346
00:18:33,920 --> 00:18:37,360
She can sing for you
and that will relieve your pain.

347
00:18:38,680 --> 00:18:40,520
I think you didn't hear me.

348
00:18:41,600 --> 00:18:43,520
She used to put my head in her lap

349
00:18:43,600 --> 00:18:46,200
and caress my forehead
while singing.

350
00:18:46,400 --> 00:18:48,880
That's how my pain went away.

351
00:18:49,360 --> 00:18:51,480
She can sing on the phone.

352
00:18:51,920 --> 00:18:54,880
But who will caress my forehead.

353
00:18:55,040 --> 00:18:56,720
You're right about that.

354
00:18:57,120 --> 00:18:59,320
What should we do?
- Why don't you

355
00:19:00,800 --> 00:19:03,760
caress my forehead and sing to me?

356
00:19:04,880 --> 00:19:08,960
No! I mean... I can sing.

357
00:19:09,360 --> 00:19:11,280
I can't caress your forehead.

358
00:19:11,440 --> 00:19:12,960
Bhabhi...

359
00:19:15,880 --> 00:19:18,400
Mr Tiwari, don't get frustrated.

360
00:19:18,680 --> 00:19:20,440
Try to understand my situation.

361
00:19:20,520 --> 00:19:23,520
The oil you put in your hair

362
00:19:23,800 --> 00:19:28,080
will make my fingers sticky
and singing.

363
00:19:30,080 --> 00:19:32,320
It's out of the question.
My sari will be ruined.

364
00:19:32,400 --> 00:19:34,000
Get rid of the sari.
- What?

365
00:19:34,120 --> 00:19:37,720
I mean... Forget about the sari.
I'll wash it for you.

366
00:19:38,240 --> 00:19:39,400
For now...

367
00:19:40,840 --> 00:19:43,520
Let me put my head in your lap
and please sing to me!

368
00:19:43,600 --> 00:19:45,280
Please don't cry.

369
00:19:45,760 --> 00:19:46,880
Oh, God!

370
00:19:46,960 --> 00:19:49,360
Mr Tiwari, please don't cry.

371
00:19:50,680 --> 00:19:52,080
Let's give it a try.

372
00:19:52,640 --> 00:19:57,120
By the way, which song did your mom
sing to you?

373
00:19:58,240 --> 00:20:01,840
"My beloved says something to me."

374
00:20:01,920 --> 00:20:05,200
"But I don't know what it is."

375
00:20:05,600 --> 00:20:09,160
"My heart dances with joy!"

376
00:20:09,320 --> 00:20:13,680
"But I don't know why."

377
00:20:15,760 --> 00:20:16,800
Wow!

378
00:20:18,800 --> 00:20:23,960
I mean... Your mom used to sing
romantic songs to relieve your pain!

379
00:20:24,240 --> 00:20:26,240
Haven't you met my mom?

380
00:20:26,560 --> 00:20:29,440
Does she look like someone
who would sing a lullaby?

381
00:20:29,640 --> 00:20:31,800
She used to sing what she knew.

382
00:20:32,080 --> 00:20:34,080
You can sing whatever song you know.

383
00:20:36,480 --> 00:20:37,720
Alright.

384
00:20:37,800 --> 00:20:41,000
Come on. Let's give it a try.
Let's go.

385
00:20:45,560 --> 00:20:47,120
He's here!
- Run!

386
00:20:50,760 --> 00:20:53,480
Why are you scared?
I won't bite you.

387
00:20:53,800 --> 00:20:55,600
I'm wearing a muzzle.

388
00:20:57,160 --> 00:20:58,360
Hi, sir.

389
00:20:58,640 --> 00:21:00,160
Greetings, Vibhuti sir.

390
00:21:02,440 --> 00:21:03,720
Hello, everyone!

391
00:21:04,680 --> 00:21:07,240
Hey! What's wrong?

392
00:21:07,920 --> 00:21:09,600
Why are you scared?

393
00:21:09,920 --> 00:21:13,000
He won't bite you. He doesn't bite.

394
00:21:13,200 --> 00:21:14,360
Sir.

395
00:21:15,440 --> 00:21:18,400
Vibhuti sir, I'm sure
this muzzle is uncomfortable.

396
00:21:18,480 --> 00:21:20,000
You have no idea.

397
00:21:20,080 --> 00:21:23,920
I feel as if someone has
trapped my breath in a cage.

398
00:21:25,120 --> 00:21:28,720
In that case, we will
free you from this misery.

399
00:21:28,960 --> 00:21:30,280
What did you say?

400
00:21:30,960 --> 00:21:32,600
Are you threatening to kill me?

401
00:21:32,760 --> 00:21:34,040
No, sir.

402
00:21:34,400 --> 00:21:37,560
Actually, you are
very important to us.

403
00:21:37,760 --> 00:21:40,120
So, we are ready
to take off your muzzle.

404
00:21:40,280 --> 00:21:43,400
But we have a special
offer for you.

405
00:21:44,440 --> 00:21:46,160
Why are you being so nice to me?

406
00:21:46,240 --> 00:21:48,960
Because you can do something
for us in return.

407
00:21:49,080 --> 00:21:50,360
What do you want me to do?

408
00:21:50,440 --> 00:21:53,280
We don't have any proof that says

409
00:21:53,480 --> 00:21:55,960
you were the one who bit us
the last time. - I see.

410
00:21:56,040 --> 00:21:58,840
Our boss will pay us compensation
only if he gets proof.

411
00:21:59,680 --> 00:22:01,520
Our only request is
that you bite us gently.

412
00:22:01,840 --> 00:22:05,280
Consider us your cute little pups.
- Right.

413
00:22:05,680 --> 00:22:07,280
We will make a video.

414
00:22:07,400 --> 00:22:10,000
We will show it to Mr Tiwari
and get compensation from him.

415
00:22:10,560 --> 00:22:13,000
I will get 50%.
- He wants...

416
00:22:15,880 --> 00:22:19,080
Excuse me! Why would you get 50%?

417
00:22:19,280 --> 00:22:20,520
Why should we give you a share?

418
00:22:20,600 --> 00:22:24,480
Because I will bite your
dirty and stinky skin

419
00:22:24,720 --> 00:22:28,360
with my well-brushed
and well-cared-for teeth!

420
00:22:28,640 --> 00:22:30,240
That's very unhygienic.

421
00:22:31,800 --> 00:22:33,840
What if I contract an infection?

422
00:22:34,520 --> 00:22:36,160
What will happen to me?

423
00:22:36,240 --> 00:22:38,120
I don't even have insurance.

424
00:22:41,920 --> 00:22:44,800
It's okay, sir. We're ready.

425
00:22:45,400 --> 00:22:47,880
I will remove the muzzle.
You be ready.

426
00:22:47,960 --> 00:22:49,000
I'm ready.

427
00:22:52,400 --> 00:22:54,040
Say it.

428
00:22:58,600 --> 00:23:01,080
Vibhuti is useless!

429
00:23:03,160 --> 00:23:06,920
You live off the scraps
that Bhabhi Ji throws at you!

430
00:23:11,480 --> 00:23:14,200
Oh, God!

431
00:23:14,760 --> 00:23:18,080
Please bite gently!

432
00:23:18,360 --> 00:23:20,320
Tika... Are you okay, Tika?

433
00:23:20,400 --> 00:23:22,440
Tillu!

434
00:23:22,640 --> 00:23:27,080
He is going to bit off
a chunk of my thick skin!

435
00:23:28,360 --> 00:23:30,560
Gently! Gently!

436
00:23:34,160 --> 00:23:35,440
We got the video.

437
00:23:36,680 --> 00:23:38,600
Was the shot okay?
- It was great.
